casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 10, 1993

MERIT DOCKET

92-2290. State ex rel. Fields v. Ohio Adult Parole Auth.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent, on motion to file answer instanter, and on motion to amend complaint. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright and Resnick, JJ., concur. F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., would deny the writ.
